Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
fix_pg_antenna(25.10)                                    fix_pg_antenna(25.10)

Name
       fix_pg_antenna  -  Fixes  the antenna violations on PG nets of backside
       layers

Syntax
       fix_pg_antenna

       [-help]

       [-selected]

       Fixes the antenna violations on PG nets of backside layers.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes the type  and  default
              information for each  fix_pg_antenna parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man fix_pg_antenna

       -selected
              Fixes antenna violations for selected nets only.

              Note:  When this parameter is not specified, the diode insertion
              is applied to all backside PG antenna violations.

              Type: bool, optional

Examples
       The following command fixes the antenna violations on the  selected  PG
       nets.

       fix_pg_antenna -selected

